# Bundled top-100k local fallback list (ADR 0070 §5).
#
# Format: one uppercase SHA-1 hex digest of a known-breached password per
# line. Lines starting with '#' or empty lines are ignored. The SHA-1
# format mirrors HIBP's "Pwned Passwords v2" download so the file is a
# drop-in for an offline-mirrored corpus.
#
# This bundled list is a reduced top-N seed (~50 entries) — enough to
# exercise the §5 fail-shape end to end and to gate the absolute-worst
# passwords offline. Operations that need full top-100k coverage
# replace this file with a pre-downloaded corpus on deploy; the adapter
# loads whatever is here at startup.
